data.value:
SET DATEFORMAT DMY
DECLARE @Nam as INT DECLARE @Thang as nvarchar(7) DECLARE @DenNgay AS DATETIME
SET @Nam = {[@Nam]} SET @Thang = '{[@Thang]}' SET @DenNgay = '{[@DenNgay]}'
SELECT ID,TenHoaDon,DVT,KhoThue,KhoThuc,(KhoThue-KhoThuc)ChenhLech
FROM
(
SELECT ID,TenHoaDon, (SELECT TEN FROM TENDONVITINH WHERE ID = VATTU.IDDonvitinh)DVT,
-- so luong ton kho thue den thoi ky ( -- so luong khai bao ton dau ky ISNULL((select DauKy from tonkhovattuthue where IdVatTu = VATTU.ID and Nam = @Nam),0) + -- cong voi so nhap kho dau ky ISNULL((SELECT SUM(CHUNGTUCHITIET.SoLuong) FROM CHUNGTU LEFT OUTER JOIN CHUNGTUCHITIET ON CHUNGTU.Id = CHUNGTUCHITIET.Id_CT WHERE CHUNGTUCHITIET.IdVatTu = VATTU.ID AND CHUNGTU.LOAICT IN (2) AND CHUNGTU.GhiSo = 1 AND YEAR(CHUNGTU.NgayHD) = @Nam AND CHUNGTUCHITIET.ButToan = 1 AND Convert(datetime,Convert(nvarchar,CHUNGTU.NgayHD,103),103) <= @DenNgay),0) - -- tru di so xuat kho dau ky ISNULL((SELECT SUM(CHUNGTUCHITIET.SoLuong) FROM CHUNGTU LEFT OUTER JOIN CHUNGTUCHITIET ON CHUNGTU.Id = CHUNGTUCHITIET.Id_CT WHERE CHUNGTUCHITIET.IdVatTu = VATTU.ID AND CHUNGTU.LOAICT IN (1) AND CHUNGTU.GhiSo = 1 AND YEAR(CHUNGTU.NgayHD) = @Nam AND CHUNGTUCHITIET.ButToan = 1 AND Convert(datetime,Convert(nvarchar,CHUNGTU.NgayHD,103),103) <= @DenNgay),0) )KhoThue,
-- so luong ton kho thuc te ( ISNULL((SELECT SUM(NHAPKHO.SoLuong) FROM NHAPKHO RIGHT OUTER JOIN PHIEUNHAPKHO ON NHAPKHO.Sophieu = PHIEUNHAPKHO.Sophieu WHERE NHAPKHO.IdVattu = VATTU.ID AND YEAR(PHIEUNHAPKHO.NgayThang) <= @DenNgay),0) - ISNULL((SELECT SUM(XUATKHO.SoLuong) FROM XUATKHO RIGHT OUTER JOIN PHIEUXUATKHO ON XUATKHO.Sophieu = PHIEUXUATKHO.Sophieu WHERE XUATKHO.IdVattu = VATTU.ID AND YEAR(PHIEUXUATKHO.NgayThang) <= @DenNgay {[DK_LOC_2]} -- AND PHIEUXUATKHO.Congtrinh = 0 ),0)
)KhoThuc
FROM VATTU WHERE 1 = 1 {[DK_LOC_1]}
)TBL WHERE KhoThue <> 0 OR KhoThuc <> 0
ORDER BY TenHoaDon
